islike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T14:46:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾條生路行下啦 食支煙啫 火車頭就話抵屌 企係垃圾桶隔離都屌？</blockquote><br />\n我唔係話要全面禁煙(雖然我好撚想)<br />\n<br />\n但至少都好似你咁會搵垃圾桶同對準個煙灰缸，而唔係周街食食到周地灰，甚至啲灰吹到落其他人嘅衣物上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd5274c249b1f74160ad7d062944f0e3317737f","tid":58063,"uid":39218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T14:50:27.000Z","msg":"有8個煙剷留低負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不服來辨，唔好做埋曬啲淨係留低負皮就走嘅懦夫行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n絕對可以理性討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}